---
// ResumeChat - conversational resume modal.
// Triggered by any element with `data-resume-chat` (or matching href="#resume-chat").
// Responses are first-person ("我") to feel like Lei is replying through an AI client.

const suggestions = [
  '你是谁？',
  'Cairn 是什么？',
  'Lumen Brief 怎么用？',
  'MCPort 有什么用？',
  '做过哪些项目？',
  '怎么联系你？'
];

// Initial greeting shown when the chat opens
const greeting =
  '你好，我是 Lei。10+ 年工程经验，最近主要做 AI 工具、MCP/RAG、信息自动化和桌面效率工具。\n\n我喜欢把想法做成能跑的东西：有入口、有命令、有发布记录，也有继续打磨的空间。你可以问我的项目、技术栈、合作方式或联系方式。';
---

<div class="resume-chat" id="resume-chat" hidden aria-hidden="true" role="dialog" aria-modal="true" aria-labelledby="resume-chat-title">
  <div class="resume-chat-backdrop" data-resume-chat-close></div>

  <div class="resume-chat-window" role="document">
    <!-- Animated gradient border -->
    <div class="window-border" aria-hidden="true"></div>

    <!-- Header -->
    <header class="chat-header">
      <div class="chat-identity">
        <div class="chat-avatar">
          <span class="avatar-glyph">L</span>
          <span class="avatar-ring" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        </div>
        <div class="chat-meta">
          <h2 class="chat-name" id="resume-chat-title">
            Lei <span class="chat-model">· lei-1.0</span>
          </h2>
          <div class="chat-status">
            <span class="status-led"></span>
            在线 · 项目、经验、合作方式
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <button class="chat-close" type="button" data-resume-chat-close aria-label="关闭对话">
        <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round">
          <line x1="18" y1="6" x2="6" y2="18"></line>
          <line x1="6" y1="6" x2="18" y2="18"></line>
        </svg>
      </button>
    </header>

    <!-- Messages -->
    <main class="chat-body" id="resume-chat-body" aria-live="polite">
      <!-- messages get injected here -->
    </main>
    <script type="application/json" id="resume-chat-greeting" set:html={JSON.stringify(greeting)}></script>

    <!-- Suggestion chips -->
    <div class="chat-suggestions" id="resume-chat-suggestions">
      {suggestions.map((s) => (
        <button type="button" class="suggestion-chip" data-suggestion={s}>{s}</button>
      ))}
    </div>

    <!-- Input -->
    <form class="chat-input" id="resume-chat-form" autocomplete="off">
      <div class="input-wrap">
        <span class="input-prefix" aria-hidden="true">›</span>
        <input
          type="text"
          id="resume-chat-input"
          name="message"
          placeholder="问项目、技术栈或合作方式 …"
          aria-label="输入问题"
          autocomplete="off"
        />
      </div>
      <button type="submit" class="send-btn" aria-label="发送">
        <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <line x1="22" y1="2" x2="11" y2="13"></line>
          <polygon points="22 2 15 22 11 13 2 9 22 2"></polygon>
        </svg>
      </button>
    </form>

    <div class="chat-footer">
      <span class="footer-hint">想深入聊具体项目 · 直接 <button type="button" class="footer-link" data-resume-chat-action="contact">看联系方式</button></span>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  /* === Overlay === */
  .resume-chat {
    position: fixed;
    inset: 0;
    z-index: 1000;
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    opacity: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
    transition: opacity 0.35s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
  }

  .resume-chat[data-open='true'] {
    opacity: 1;
    pointer-events: auto;
  }

  .resume-chat[hidden] {
    display: none;
  }

  .resume-chat-backdrop {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background:
      radial-gradient(900px 600px at 30% 20%, rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.18), transparent 60%),
      radial-gradient(700px 500px at 80% 80%, rgba(34, 211, 238, 0.14), transparent 60%),
      rgba(8, 8, 14, 0.78);
    backdrop-filter: blur(18px);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(18px);
  }

  /* === Window === */
  .resume-chat-window {
    position: relative;
    width: min(720px, 100%);
    height: min(720px, calc(100vh - 3rem));
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    background:
      linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(20, 20, 30, 0.88), rgba(12, 12, 18, 0.92));
    border-radius: 1.5rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.22);
    box-shadow:
      0 30px 80px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.55),
      0 0 60px rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.12);
    overflow: hidden;
    transform: translateY(16px) scale(0.98);
    opacity: 0;
    transition: transform 0.35s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1), opacity 0.3s;
    isolation: isolate;
  }

  .resume-chat[data-open='true'] .resume-chat-window {
    transform: translateY(0) scale(1);
    opacity: 1;
  }

  /* Slowly flowing gradient border */
  .window-border {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    border-radius: inherit;
    padding: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg,
      rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.5),
      rgba(34, 211, 238, 0.4),
      rgba(236, 72, 153, 0.4),
      rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.5));
    background-size: 300% 300%;
    -webkit-mask:
      linear-gradient(#000 0 0) content-box,
      linear-gradient(#000 0 0);
    -webkit-mask-composite: xor;
            mask-composite: exclude;
    pointer-events: none;
    animation: window-border-flow 12s linear infinite;
    opacity: 0.7;
  }

  @keyframes window-border-flow {
    0% { background-position: 0% 50%; }
    100% { background-position: 300% 50%; }
  }

  /* === Header === */
  .chat-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 1rem;
    padding: 1.1rem 1.4rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02);
  }

  .chat-identity {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.85rem;
    min-width: 0;
  }

  .chat-avatar {
    position: relative;
    width: 42px;
    height: 42px;
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6366f1, #22d3ee);
    flex-shrink: 0;
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08), 0 8px 24px rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.35);
  }

  .avatar-glyph {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', ui-monospace, monospace;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: white;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  .avatar-ring {
    position: absolute;
    inset: -4px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    border: 1.5px dashed rgba(34, 211, 238, 0.35);
    animation: avatar-spin 14s linear infinite;
  }

  @keyframes avatar-spin {
    to { transform: rotate(360deg); }
  }

  .chat-meta {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.15rem;
    min-width: 0;
  }

  .chat-name {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .chat-model {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', ui-monospace, monospace;
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--text-tertiary);
  }

  .chat-status {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--text-tertiary);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.4rem;
  }

  .status-led {
    width: 6px;
    height: 6px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: #22d3ee;
    box-shadow: 0 0 8px #22d3ee;
    animation: led-pulse 2s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  @keyframes led-pulse {
    0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
    50% { opacity: 0.4; }
  }

  .chat-close {
    width: 36px;
    height: 36px;
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
    border-radius: 10px;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.2s;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .chat-close:hover {
    background: rgba(236, 72, 153, 0.12);
    border-color: rgba(236, 72, 153, 0.3);
    color: #ec4899;
  }

  /* === Body / Messages === */
  .chat-body {
    flex: 1;
    overflow-y: auto;
    padding: 1.5rem 1.4rem 1rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
    scroll-behavior: smooth;
  }

  .chat-body::-webkit-scrollbar {
    width: 6px;
  }
  .chat-body::-webkit-scrollbar-track {
    background: transparent;
  }
  .chat-body::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
    border-radius: 3px;
  }

  .message {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    max-width: 100%;
    animation: msg-in 0.35s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
  }

  @keyframes msg-in {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(8px); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }

  .message.user {
    justify-content: flex-end;
  }

  .msg-avatar {
    width: 30px;
    height: 30px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', ui-monospace, monospace;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 4px;
  }

  .message.ai .msg-avatar {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6366f1, #22d3ee);
    color: white;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.35);
  }

  .msg-bubble {
    padding: 0.85rem 1rem;
    border-radius: 14px;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
    white-space: pre-wrap;
    word-break: break-word;
    max-width: 85%;
  }

  .message.ai .msg-bubble {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
    color: var(--text-primary);
    border-top-left-radius: 4px;
  }

  .message.user .msg-bubble {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg,
      rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.25),
      rgba(34, 211, 238, 0.18));
    border: 1px solid rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.3);
    color: var(--text-primary);
    border-top-right-radius: 4px;
  }

  /* Inline code-ish styling within bubbles */
  .msg-bubble code {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', ui-monospace, monospace;
    font-size: 0.85em;
    padding: 0.05em 0.4em;
    background: rgba(34, 211, 238, 0.12);
    border-radius: 4px;
    color: #22d3ee;
  }

  .msg-bubble strong {
    color: var(--accent-cyan);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  /* Blinking caret while AI is streaming */
  .msg-bubble.streaming::after {
    content: '▍';
    color: #22d3ee;
    margin-left: 2px;
    animation: caret-blink 0.9s step-end infinite;
  }

  @keyframes caret-blink {
    50% { opacity: 0; }
  }

  /* Typing indicator (three dots) */
  .typing-dots {
    display: inline-flex;
    gap: 4px;
    align-items: center;
    height: 1.2em;
  }
  .typing-dots span {
    width: 6px;
    height: 6px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--text-tertiary);
    animation: typing-bounce 1.4s infinite ease-in-out;
  }
  .typing-dots span:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.15s; }
  .typing-dots span:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 0.3s; }

  @keyframes typing-bounce {
    0%, 60%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); opacity: 0.4; }
    30% { transform: translateY(-4px); opacity: 1; }
  }

  /* === Suggestions === */
  .chat-suggestions {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    padding: 0 1.4rem 0.75rem;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
    padding-top: 0.85rem;
  }

  .suggestion-chip {
    padding: 0.4rem 0.85rem;
    background: rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.08);
    border: 1px solid rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.18);
    border-radius: 999px;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.2s;
    font-family: inherit;
  }

  .suggestion-chip:hover {
    background: rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.16);
    border-color: rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.4);
    color: var(--text-primary);
    transform: translateY(-1px);
  }

  /* === Input === */
  .chat-input {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.6rem;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.4rem 0.9rem;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02);
  }

  .input-wrap {
    flex: 1;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    padding: 0.7rem 1rem;
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.35);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
    border-radius: 12px;
    transition: border-color 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
  }

  .input-wrap:focus-within {
    border-color: rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.5);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.12);
  }

  .input-prefix {
    color: #22d3ee;
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', ui-monospace, monospace;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .input-wrap input {
    flex: 1;
    background: transparent;
    border: none;
    outline: none;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    font-family: inherit;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    min-width: 0;
  }

  .input-wrap input::placeholder {
    color: var(--text-tertiary);
  }

  .send-btn {
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    width: 44px;
    height: 44px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6366f1, #22d3ee);
    border: none;
    border-radius: 12px;
    color: white;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s, opacity 0.2s;
    box-shadow: 0 6px 18px rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.35);
  }

  .send-btn:hover {
    transform: translateY(-1px);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 22px rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.5);
  }

  .send-btn:disabled {
    opacity: 0.4;
    cursor: not-allowed;
    transform: none;
  }

  /* === Footer === */
  .chat-footer {
    padding: 0.6rem 1.4rem 0.9rem;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
  }

  .footer-hint {
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    color: var(--text-tertiary);
    text-align: center;
    display: block;
  }

  .footer-link {
    background: none;
    border: none;
    color: var(--accent-cyan);
    cursor: pointer;
    padding: 0;
    font: inherit;
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-decoration-color: rgba(34, 211, 238, 0.4);
    text-underline-offset: 2px;
  }

  /* === Mobile === */
  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .resume-chat {
      padding: 0.5rem;
    }
    .resume-chat-window {
      height: calc(100vh - 1rem);
      border-radius: 1rem;
    }
    .chat-header {
      padding: 0.9rem 1rem;
    }
    .chat-body {
      padding: 1rem 1rem 0.5rem;
    }
    .chat-suggestions,
    .chat-input,
    .chat-footer {
      padding-left: 1rem;
      padding-right: 1rem;
    }
    .msg-bubble {
      max-width: 90%;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }
  }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .avatar-ring,
    .window-border,
    .status-led {
      animation: none !important;
    }
  }
</style>

<script>
  // === Intent matching & response bank ===
  type Intent = {
    keys: RegExp[];
    answer: string | (() => string);
    followups?: string[];
  };

  const intents: Intent[] = [
    {
      keys: [/^(你好|您好|hi|hello|hey|嗨|在吗|哈喽)/i],
      answer:
        '你好，我是 **Lei**。我有 10+ 年工程经验，最近主要做 AI 工具、MCP/RAG、信息自动化和桌面效率工具。\n\n我比较在意一件事：想法最后要落到能用的工具里。你可以问我具体项目、技术栈、合作方式，或者直接看 GitHub。',
      followups: ['你是谁？', 'Cairn 是什么？', '你的技术栈']
    },
    {
      keys: [/你是谁|介绍.*你|介绍.*自己|about you|who are you|介绍下/i],
      answer:
        '我是 **Lei**（钱磊），上海大学本科，10+ 年研发经验。\n\n我的优势不是单点技术，而是把一个想法做成能运行的工具：需求拆解、前端体验、后端接口、CLI、自动化、测试、发布和文档都能覆盖。\n\n最近我主要做几类作品：\n\n• **Cairn / DocsGraph**：让 coding agent 更准确地读取项目文档\n• **Lumen Brief**：把 AI 信息源自动整理到个人知识库\n• **MCPort**：把 HTTP API 配置成 MCP tools\n• **Sotto / Red Green Light**：把本地 AI CLI 的内容和状态做成桌面体验\n\n我不太想把自己包装成一个很抽象的 title。我的特点更像是：看见一个流程不顺，就会想办法把它做成工具。',
      followups: ['Cairn 是什么？', 'Lumen Brief 怎么用？', 'MCPort 有什么用？']
    },
    {
      keys: [/cairn|docsgraph|文档|知识图谱|rag|检索/i],
      answer:
        '**Cairn / DocsGraph** 是我做的本地文档索引和 MCP 工具。\n\n它来自一个很实际的痛点：AI coding agent 经常需要读项目文档，但整篇塞进去又贵又乱。Cairn 会把文档拆成目录树、摘要、实体、交叉引用和向量索引，再通过 MCP 暴露 `search_documents`、`repo_context`、`repo_graph` 等工具。\n\n我喜欢它的原因是，它不炫。它只是让模型少猜一点，让人少复制一点，让上下文更像工程材料而不是聊天素材。',
      followups: ['MCPort 有什么用？', '你的技术栈']
    },
    {
      keys: [/lumen|aibrief|brief|简报|信息源|notebooklm|obsidian|yo/i],
      answer:
        '**Lumen Brief** 是我的 AI 信息自动化项目。\n\n它聚合 AI 研究、开源模型、工具、社区讨论和岗位趋势，输出每日卡片、HTML 预览、Obsidian 笔记、NotebookLM 资料包和来源清单。\n\n这个项目不是做资讯站，而是解决个人知识管理中的真实问题：每天看很多材料，怎样沉淀成以后能检索、能复盘、能继续写作的资料。',
      followups: ['Cairn 是什么？', '做过哪些项目？']
    },
    {
      keys: [/mcport|http.*mcp|openapi|api|tool calling|工具调用/i],
      answer:
        '**MCPort** 是一个 HTTP API 到 MCP Tool 的桥接和管理服务。\n\n很多现有 API 本来就能完成任务，只是 AI 客户端不方便直接调用。MCPort 的做法是：在 Web UI 里配置 endpoint、参数、鉴权和测试请求，再由 `/mcp` 运行时把它们暴露成 typed tools。\n\n它体现的是很实用的 AI 落地能力：把已有系统能力接入模型工具调用，而不是重新造一套服务。',
      followups: ['Cairn 是什么？', '你的技术栈']
    },
    {
      keys: [/经历|经验|履历|工作|职业|career|experience|背景|past/i],
      answer:
        '我有 10+ 年研发经验，曾在 **阿里巴巴、拼多多、美团、字节跳动** 做过大型 Web、前端工程、BFF、研发平台、自动化发布和开发者工具。\n\n这些经历最后沉成了几个习惯：\n\n• 先把复杂流程拆清楚\n• 把重复工作做成工具\n• 从界面、服务、CLI 到 CI/CD 能一路接起来\n• 原型跑通后，继续补测试、文档、发布和可维护性\n\n现在这些习惯主要落在 AI 工具链、MCP/RAG、知识自动化和桌面效率工具上。',
      followups: ['你的技术栈', '做过哪些项目？', '怎么联系你？']
    },
    {
      keys: [/技术栈|skill|stack|技能|擅长|能做什么|tech/i],
      answer:
